{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm-breadth-first-search/","result":{"data":{"site":{"id":"Site","siteMetadata":{"title":"Financiest"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"fd15e3d5-82a8-5810-b197-00dffd83263d","excerpt":"Breadth first search is an algorithm used for searching through all the nodes in a graph or tree structure. Python implementation:","html":"<p>Breadth first search is an algorithm used for searching through all the nodes in a graph or tree structure.</p>\n<p>Python implementation: </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># Time: O(node + edge)</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Space: O(node)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">breadthFirstSearch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> resultList<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># Create a queue, a FIFO strucutre, to contain</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># all nodes that will be processed</span>\n    queue <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">len</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>queue<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        current <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> queue<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pop<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        resultList<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>append<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>current<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\"># Add child nodes to the queue</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> child <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> current<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>children<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n            queue<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>append<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>child<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> resultList</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Algorithm - Breadth first search","date":"May 06, 2015","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm-breadth-first-search/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm-depth-first-search copy/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Algorithm - Depth first search"}},"next":null}}}